name: Attuned_Overwhelming_Force_D
display_help: UNIQUE -- No more than 1 enhancement of this type may be slotted by a character. Enhances the damage of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Damage.Scale}%, reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.RechargeTime.Scale}% and reduces endurance cost by {Boost.Attrib.Endurance.Scale}% .
